com.vmware.nsx.transport_nodes

Class TransportNodesFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx.transport_nodes.TransportNodesFactory

  • public class TransportNodesFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    TransportNodesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx.transport_nodes package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
